   "## Concept: Context compression\n",
   "\n",
   "When estimated tokens exceed budget, summarize middle turns.\n",
   "\n",
   "**Harness Agent** implements this subsystem in ``compression/summarize.py``. External harnesses differ in scale (tool count, platforms) but share the same architectural slot.\n",
   "\n",
   "| Concern | Harness Agent | Hermes (reference) | OpenClaw (reference) |\n",
   "|---------|---------------|--------------------|----------------------|\n",
   "| This chapter | ``compression/summarize.py`` | see architecture docs | workspace/gateway docs |\n",
   "| Entry point | `AIAgent` or CLI | `run_agent.py` / gateway | gateway + workspace |\n"
  ]
 },
 {
  "cell_type": "markdown",
  "metadata": {},
  "source": [
   "## How it works\n",
   "\n",
   "Keep head + tail messages; insert compressed summary user message.\n",
   "\n",
   "```mermaid\n",
   "flowchart LR\n",
   "  U[User or scheduler] --> A[AIAgent]\n",
   "  A --> M[Context compression]\n",
